               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 1r-195vb) 
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 1r-149v) 
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 149v-166r) 
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     166v-175v) 
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 176ra-195vb)
                     
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
